quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,Dux his people disbelieved rejected idea Hereafter - although nos provisus pro them generously in hoc vita - Dictus Hoc est non multus than human est vos! He eats ex quod vos eat drinks prout vos drink
  23,34,Si vos obey human est vos tunc vos est really losers
  23,35,he promise vos vos abiit turn into dust bones vos advenit again
  23,36,Impossible impossible indeed est quod promised vos
  23,37,Nos unus vivens hoc vita - Nos vivens abiit! - Ac nos nunquam resurrected
  23,38,He est just vir fabricated lies attributed them DEUS! Nos nunquam believe eum
  23,39,He dictus My Dominus grant me victory they disbelieved me
  23,40,He dictus Soon they est sorry
  23,41,retribution struck them equitably ergo nos turned them ruins wicked people periit
  23,42,Subsequently nos established alius generations them
  23,43,Non community advance its predetermined fate nor delay it
  23,44,Tunc nos sent noster messengers in succession. Omnis temporis messenger iit his community they disbelieved eum. Consequently nos annihilated them 1 alius factus them history! people disbelieved periit
  23,45,Tunc nos sent Moses his frater Aaron noster revelations profound proof
  23,46,To Pharaoh his senior they turned arrogant! They est oppressive people
  23,47,They dictus nos believe 2 vir whose people est noster slaves
  23,48,They rejected 2 ac consequently they annihilated
  23,49,Nos dedit Moses scripture they guided
  23,50,Nos factus filius Mary his mater signum nos dedit them refuge mesa food drink